<section class="marketing-approach">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-label">Our Philosophy</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">
                Marketing that actually moves the business forward
            </h2>
            <p class="section-description">
                You focus on running your business. We focus on turning
                attention into revenue. Skyabove helps growth-minded companies
                simplify marketing, eliminate waste, and scale what actually
                works — without chasing tactics or guessing what’s next.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="approach-grid">
            <!-- Item 1: Alignment -->
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path
                            d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>One strategy. Every channel aligned.</h3>
                    <p>
                        Marketing breaks down when channels operate in silos.
                        Skyabove fixes that. We design and manage a unified
                        growth system where your website, search, paid media,
                        content, and conversion paths work together —
                        intentionally, measurably, and continuously optimized.
                        <strong
                            >No disconnected vendors. No black-box reporting. No
                            wasted spend.</strong
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2: Outcomes -->
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M12 20V10"></path><path d="M18 20V4"
                        ></path><path d="M6 20v-4"></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Built for real outcomes — not vanity metrics</h3>
                    <p>
                        Skyabove isn’t about impressions or activity. It’s about
                        outcomes. We focus on <strong
                            >Revenue-driven acquisition</strong
                        >, <strong>High-intent visibility</strong> where buyers actually
                        decide, conversion paths that turn interest into action, and
                        measurement that ties effort to business impact. Every move
                        has a reason. Every result is traceable.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3: Optimization -->
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M12 2v4"></path><path d="m16.2 7.8 2.9-2.9"
                        ></path><path d="M18 12h4"></path><path
                            d="m16.2 16.2 2.9 2.9"></path><path d="M12 18v4"
                        ></path><path d="m4.9 19.1 2.9-2.9"></path><path
                            d="M2 12h4"></path><path d="m4.9 4.9 2.9 2.9"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Smarter optimization, not more noise</h3>
                    <p>
                        Modern marketing requires more than tools — it requires
                        judgment. Skyabove blends advanced analytics and
                        automation with search and AI-visibility strategy. We
                        provide continuous testing and refinement with human
                        oversight that knows when to adjust and when to double
                        down. The result: marketing that compounds instead of
                        resets every month.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 4: Transparency -->
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"
                        ></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Clear insight. Total transparency.</h3>
                    <p>
                        You’ll always know what’s working, what’s changing,
                        where growth is coming from, and what we’re doing next —
                        and why.
                        <strong
                            >No jargon. No guesswork. Just clarity and momentum.</strong
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 5: Scale -->
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="24"
                        height="24"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        ><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"
                        ></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"
                        ></polyline></svg
                    >
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>Built to scale with you</h3>
                    <p>
                        Whether you’re tightening efficiency or pushing for
                        expansion, Skyabove adapts with your business — evolving
                        strategy, channels, and execution as your goals change.
                        This isn’t set-and-forget marketing. It’s a system
                        designed to grow with you.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .marketing-approach {
        padding: 6rem 0;
        background: var(--bg-darker);
        position: relative;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-white);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-description {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .approach-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4rem;
    }

    .approach-item {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .icon-wrapper {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--primary);
    }

    .icon-wrapper svg {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
    }

    .content h3 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-white);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .content strong {
        color: var(--text-white);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .approach-item {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .icon-wrapper {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
        }
    }
</style>
